\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14834826 DT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1072918\charrsid5596047 Oh well, I had - I had to make some clothes and that sort of thing to go out in, didn't I. I made some clothes - yes, by hand.
