\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6519033 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1072918\charrsid5596047 That's quite often isn't it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14834826 DT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1072918\charrsid5596047 Yes.
