\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6519033 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1072918\charrsid5596047 Was she the only person who helped your mother with the housework at that time?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14834826 DT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1072918\charrsid5596047 Yes.
