\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6519033 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1072918\charrsid5596047 What were here duties?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14834826 DT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1072918\charrsid5596047 I remember - she'd be doing - she'd do the beds - and the floors. Mind you you didn't scrub them or anything I meant
