\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6519033 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1072918\charrsid5596047 Was she in any way responsible for you - did she have to keep an eye on you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14834826 DT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1072918\charrsid5596047 No. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6519033 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1072918\charrsid5596047 Did she ever take you to school?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14834826 DT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1072918\charrsid5596047 No, I was - of course when mother and father went out she would be - have to be there when I went to bed out otherwise she didn't.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6519033 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1072918\charrsid5596047 Did she wash your - no you had a washerwoman didn't you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14834826 DT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1072918\charrsid5596047 Yes. Yes, she did the washing.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6519033 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1072918\charrsid5596047 Did she bath you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14834826 DT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1072918\charrsid5596047 No. I think I was bathing myself by that time.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6519033 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1072918\charrsid5596047 She didn't really have much personal things to do?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14834826 DT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1072918\charrsid5596047 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6519033 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1072918\charrsid5596047 She didn't eat with you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14834826 DT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1072918\charrsid5596047 No. Except as I say when dad wasn't she - she would eat with mother and I.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6519033 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1072918\charrsid5596047 A cup of tea?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14834826 DT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1072918\charrsid5596047 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6519033 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1072918\charrsid5596047 Not a meal?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14834826 DT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1072918\charrsid5596047 No. Not the meal.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6519033 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1072918\charrsid5596047 And so where would she eat?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14834826 DT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1072918\charrsid5596047 Well, we had a very large kitchen and a large scullery off - she had hers in the kitchen you see.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6519033 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1072918\charrsid5596047 What was she like - how did you get on with her?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14834826 DT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1072918\charrsid5596047 Very well - I liked her very much. She was neat and dark.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6519033 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1072918\charrsid5596047 Did you have much to do with her?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14834826 DT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1072918\charrsid5596047 No - very little. I was mainly reading.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6519033 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1072918\charrsid5596047 How did she address your mother?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14834826 DT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1072918\charrsid5596047 Madame.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6519033 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1072918\charrsid5596047 And she called you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14834826 DT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1072918\charrsid5596047 Doris.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6519033 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1072918\charrsid5596047 And what did she call your father?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14834826 DT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1072918\charrsid5596047 Monsie}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3754079\charrsid5596047 u}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1072918\charrsid5596047 
r. Mr Scotner.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6519033 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1072918\charrsid5596047 Could she speak English?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14834826 DT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1072918\charrsid5596047 Yes, very well.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6519033 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1072918\charrsid5596047 Do you feel that she was interested in you as a person?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14834826 DT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1072918\charrsid5596047 No, not a bit - I think she was merely - it was her job. Just a job.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6519033 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1072918\charrsid5596047 Do you know what she did with her spare time?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14834826 DT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1072918\charrsid5596047 No. Vaguely I think she probably went out and visited some French people she knew or something like that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6519033 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1072918\charrsid5596047 Did she have regular spare time?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14834826 DT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1072918\charrsid5596047 Oh yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6519033 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1072918\charrsid5596047 She knew when she'd have her days off and things?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14834826 DT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1072918\charrsid5596047 Yes, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6519033 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1072918\charrsid5596047 Was she allowed to do more or less as she liked?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14834826 DT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1072918\charrsid5596047 
Yes, providing the work was done she could do it as she - wished. I mean to say of course the beds had to be made in the morning and that sort of thing but - if she wanted to start with the back room instead of the front she could in that respect.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6519033 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1072918\charrsid5596047 Did your mother take any personal interest in her life - was she responsible - would your mother feel responsible?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14834826 DT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1072918\charrsid5596047 No, no. No, that's why I think 
she must have been round about - between twenty - six and thirty because I had a feeling she was quite old enough to look after herself.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6519033 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1072918\charrsid5596047 When you had visitors did she answer the door?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14834826 DT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1072918\charrsid5596047 Oh yes, yes, and she'd bring the things in and take them out - wait at table in that way but not in a uniform.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6519033 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1072918\charrsid5596047 She never wore uniform?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14834826 DT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1072918\charrsid5596047 No. At all.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6519033 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1072918\charrsid5596047 Did she mend the family's clothes?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14834826 DT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1072918\charrsid5596047 Oh no. Mother always did the mending - our mending.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6519033 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1072918\charrsid5596047 She didn't put to bed - she didn't eat meals with you an
d as far as you know she didn't cook them. Can you think of anything else about Annie that she did do?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14834826 DT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1072918\charrsid5596047 No. And I've an idea she left because she stopped doing what she did do. Mother told her to -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6519033 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1072918\charrsid5596047 She got slack you mean?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14834826 DT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1072918\charrsid5596047 Yes. You see moth
er helped quite a bit and I think Annie tended to expect her to help a bit more but that I'm not quite certain of but I think that was the reason.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6519033 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1072918\charrsid5596047 Did you ever go out anywhere with her?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14834826 DT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1072918\charrsid5596047 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6519033 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1072918\charrsid5596047 Never at all - not shopping?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14834826 DT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1072918\charrsid5596047 No. No. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6519033 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1072918\charrsid5596047 At Christmas when you all went to your grandparents or on holiday?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14834826 DT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1072918\charrsid5596047 Oh she wouldn't be with use then - she would have had - full wages and gone somewhere.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6519033 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1072918\charrsid5596047 So she didn't play a personal part?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14834826 DT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1072918\charrsid5596047 No, no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6519033 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1072918\charrsid5596047 Did she ever go out anywhere at all with you and your parents?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14834826 DT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1072918\charrsid5596047 No, no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6519033 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1072918\charrsid5596047 There's nothing else you can think of about her at all?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14834826 DT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1072918\charrsid5596047 No, I can't. She couldn't have made a great impression could she.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6519033 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1072918\charrsid5596047 How long was she with you for?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14834826 DT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1072918\charrsid5596047 Well, she was with us about two years.
\par }}